[July18,2022]

Dr. Alan Turing is the father of Computer Science and He was responsible for deciphering the Nazi Enigma code during World War II.
His work gave the Allies the advantages they needed to win the war in Europe and led to the development of computers.
He was the first person to conduct tests for the creation of the AI with Data Science.
He became an inspiration to people because of his brilliance from his early age.
The tests he made was the imitation game for his reasearch to predict genders through each individual's answers.
The Turing test functions to identify the difference of human and machine through intelligence.


